move1.name: Quick Attack
move1.description: The user lunges at the target with incredible speed. This move always goes first.

move2.name: Thunder Shock
move2.description: A jolt of electricity is hurled at the target. This may also leave the target with paralysis.

move3.name: Thunder Punch
move3.description: The target is punched with an electrified fist. It may also leave the target with paralysis.

move4.name: Thunder
move4.description: A wicked thunderbolt is dropped on the target to inflict damage. It may also leave the target with paralysis.
